  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies an override for a single color entry in a font's CPAL color palette.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKFontPaletteOverride` pairs a palette color index with a replacement ARGB color value. Use a collection of these overrides in <see cref="P:SkiaSharp.SKFontArguments.PaletteOverrides" /> to customize individual colors of a color font without replacing the entire palette.

## Examples

```csharp
// Override color index 0 with red
var override0 = new SKFontPaletteOverride { Index = 0, Color = (uint)SKColors.Red };

var args = new SKFontArguments
{
    PaletteIndex = 0,
    PaletteOverrides = new[] { override0 },
};
```
]]></format></remarks>
